Design custom work uniforms that get your brand seen at the job site.

Personalize your team’s look with custom workwear. Besides keeping your employees well-protected and comfortable, these custom work uniforms get your brand noticed – at the job site, the store, the office and more.

Our collection of personalized workwear includes jackets, T-shirts, heavyweight hoodies, custom construction vests, hats and more. Cover your employees in rugged, durable gear from renowned brands like Carhartt®, DRI DUCK®, ML KISHIGO ® and more.

And with VistaPrint, you can add your own touches using different decoration techniques such as embroidery, heat transfer and more. Just add them through our intuitive studio and we’ll handle the rest. And if you need a helping hand, our design experts are always ready to offer guidance along the way.

Frequently Asked Questions

A good work uniform balances functionality, comfort, professionalism and branding. For instance, custom construction vests are a go-to for job sites – keeping you visible and safe. There are also jackets, hoodies, sweatshirts, T-shirts and more – all great outfits whether you’re running a supply store, a repair shop, an electrical company and so on.

Thanks to our intuitive design studio, you can add a lot of unique touches to your custom work clothing – your logo, contact information, employees’ names and more. Not only do these touches make the uniforms unique, but they can also improve employee communication and customer service.

Our collection includes products from world-renowned brands such as Carhartt®, DRI DUCK®, MK KISHIGO® and more – subject to availability. Many of these brands are synonymous with high-quality, custom work uniforms.

There’s no minimum order quantity for most of our custom workwear collection. But if you order more, the discount increases according to the quantity of the order.

Your custom touches can be added using different decoration techniques – depending on the product itself. For starters, embroidery supports up to 12 different stitching colors for a durable, professional look. While heat transfer offers unlimited color options for a vibrant, colorful result.

You need it. We print it. You love it.

VistaPrint is here to help every step of the way.
